dc_title_s: Hydrography (Polygon and Line) Washburn County, WI 2015
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Washburn_Hydro_2015.gdb'. The features included in this geodatabase are 'Washburn_HydroLine_2015' and 'Washburn_HydroPoly_2015'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://co.washburn.wi.us/gis-data-downloads/
